Package edu.jhu.cs.oose.fall2014.group19.foodApp.server

Class Summary
AccountManager The ability to create user accounts The ability to delete user accounts.
ContactManager The ability to add a contact.
LoginManager The ability to login and logout of user account.
MealManager The ability to create,update,complete and close a meal post on the back end.
NotificationManager The ability to push notification to all contacts that are recipients of the notification and are currently available to the poster or become available to the poster before the notification expires or is closed manually by the poster.
RequestDispatcher Dispatches the management request to the appropriate handler on the back end.
